               <p>GODFREY LAZARUS. I am a <rs id="t18260914-365-viclabel2055" type="occupation">jeweller</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-365-victim1929 t18260914-365-viclabel2055"></join>; the prisoner was my <rs id="t18260914-365-deflabel2056" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-365-defend1928 t18260914-365-deflabel2056"></join>. On the 5th of August there was a fire, and the prisoner was taken on suspicion of setting the house on fire; but her innocence has been clearly proved - I afterwards searched her box, and found duplicates of this property.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-365-person1930">
                  WILLIAM 
