            . I am a pawnbroker. These articles were pawned by a woman, in the name of Drew.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written Defence, stating that she could not obtain her wages, and that Mrs. Lazarus had sent her to pawn the goods.</p>
               <p>GODFREY LAZARUS re-examined. I never sent her to pawn things. I owed her five months wages - she said she did it because her father was in distress.</p>
               <p>
            
